{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'What?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "It's... nothing. I just wanted to say... good work back there gunning down the Corrupted with the turret.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Piece of cake. You're gonna need some practice with the turret, though.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "You've got the controls down, but you keep missing your mark.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Understood, I'll try my best.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'We sure can count on you, Karenina.', 3: '12', 4: 'Nice job back there.', 5: '12'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Looks like not much has changed.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'You heard what happened, Bianca?', 3: '18', 4: "Guess she's avoiding me...", 5: '19'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Yeah, I heard everything. That's why the commandant was asked to release her.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Seems like it.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Commandant, as you know, Karenina has always been trying to get stronger.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I'm not sure why she is so persistent, but that's why she's drawn to such things.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'As for you, I think you are the strength that she seeks.', 4: '1'}
{2: "What's so great about me?", 3: '25', 4: 'You guys are the real strong ones.', 5: '25'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "You're too humble, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "We haven't had much time to fight at your side, but we can all see that there is something brilliant about you, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "And as a commandant, you're something she has never seen before.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "That's why she seeks your approval.", 4: '1'}
